Install dependency libraries on root
=============================
sudo apt-get install python3.12-dev
sudo apt-get install libssl-dev
sudo apt-get install default-libmysqlclient-dev
sudo apt-get install libmysqlclient-dev
sudo apt-get install mysql-server
sudo apt-get install mysql-client
sudo apt-get install pkg-config
sudo apt-get install build-essential

Additionalyy
sudo apt install libssl1.1 libssl1.1=1.1.1f-1ubuntu2 libssl-dev


Install mysql libraary and connectors on projects virtaul environment
==================================================================
Install these on virual environment
pip3 install mysql <=== this will not work unleass resolved using above commands.
pip install mysqlclient
pip install mysql-connector-python


Login to mysql db from linux server
========================
mysql -h ip_address -P 3306 -u username -p
mysql -h 15.207.141.145 -P 3306 -u app -p
